title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 13
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. In an eventful weekend Big Cat joined the hype circle, left it, denounced his Rydership and then went announced he was back to being a Ryder in the span of 48 hours. Rico and Dave have some tension over the promotion of the 2 new college basketball podcasts within the company. Eventually everyone works to settle the internal beefs in preparation for a big Feast Week!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
